mand-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p><script type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/kity@2.0.4/dist/kity.min.js"></script><script type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/kityminder-core@1.4.50/dist/kityminder.core.min.js"></script><script defer="true" type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.js"></script><link rel="stylesheet" type="text&#x2F;css" href="https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.css">]]></content>
      
      
